				"number": 2,
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"64478\"></a>Differentialdiagnoser vid olika typer av synfältsdefekter",
				"id": "o1_32",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Defekttyp</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Möjliga orsaker</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Horisontell begränsad skotom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">AION (ischemisk optikusneuropati), trombos eller emboli i motsvarande </div><div class=\"tableLine\">retinal kärlgren, näthinneavlossning, glaukom</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Bågformig skotom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Glaukom, grav myopi, ischemisk optikusneuropati</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Binasal defekt</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Bilateralt glaukom, retinitis pigmentosa, bilateral optikuskompression <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">(aneurysm, tumör)</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Bitemporal hemianopsi</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Chiasmakompression (hypofystumör, andra intracerebrala tumörer, </div><div class=\"tableLine\">aneurysm)</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Förstorad blind fläck</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Papillödem, staspapill, myopi, drusen i synnerven, myeliniserade nervfibrer</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Centralskotom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Makuladegeneration, toxisk eller metabolisk optikusneuropati, optikusatrofi</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Homonym hemianopsi</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Stroke, cerebrala tumörer</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Perifer synfältskonstriktion</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Glaukom, retinitis pigmentosa, centralartäremboli med bevarad centralt </div><div class=\"tableLine\">cilioretinalt kärl, funktionella störningar</div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
			},
